{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u9898\u56fe\u6392\u7248-\u7fbd\u7ffc.png?t=1728371084\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201cI'll tell you another story.\u201d</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201cThis is a story about a girl and a wish.\u201d</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201cA warm and romantic fairy tale\u2026\u201d</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u6807\u98981.png?t=1728371084\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a story about &quot;wishes&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interwoven with feelings of sadness and healing, where terrifying scenes blend with dreams.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u201cLet me fulfill your wish for you, but the corresponding price is\u2026\u201d</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, players will take on the role of a girl named Qiu Xiaoqi, waking up in a strange room. She will explore the mysterious room filled with puzzles alongside a mysterious young man with white hair, unraveling layers of mechanisms and uncovering the truth behind her loss of consciousness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u63d2\u56fe2.png?t=1728371084\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this journey full of choices and unknowns,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">players will face various challenges as they explore in a terrifying environment,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">experiencing the profound emotional journeys of the characters through memories and dreams, exploring the wishes hidden deep within their hearts.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Will this wish be fulfilled? How will this story unfold? Everything is for you to write\u2026</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u6807\u98982.png?t=1728371084\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u63d2\u56fe1.png?t=1728371084\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Immersive horror atmosphere</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every unknown fear draws you deeply into it.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Intricate puzzle design</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Creative mechanisms provide a unique exploration experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Heart-pounding storyline</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The profound emotional journeys of the characters present a moving tale.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rich sound performance</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Beautiful music and intense sound effects perfectly blend into the game atmosphere.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u6807\u98983.png?t=1728371084\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game Type:</strong> Horror Puzzle<br><strong>Number of Endings:</strong> 7 (*updated in 2024)<br><strong>Estimated Playtime: 2</strong>-4 hours</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Basic Controls:</strong><br>Movement: Arrow keys<br>Investigate/Confirm: Z/Space/Enter<br>Menu/Cancel: X/ESC<br>Save Management: F5<br>Resolution Adjustment: F6<br>Run: Shift</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u6807\u98984.png?t=1728371084\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game Author: \u79cb\u4e4b\u5fe7\u90c1</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game Artist: \u96e8\u516e</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game Publisher: Eternal Dream Studio</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For more staff, please see the in-game credits.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u6807\u98985.png?t=1728371084\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is the first horror puzzle game I developed in 2016.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It was my first time making a horror puzzle game, so I hope everyone understands if there are any shortcomings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game does not contain any jump-scare CG flashes, so there\u2019s no need to worry about being startled by CG suddenly~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game has undergone multiple tests, but if there are any remaining bugs, please report them immediately.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feedback channel: <a href=\"mailto:413228337@qq.com\">413228337@qq.com</a></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Where am I?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/869840/2dc0fef1f23a3729e5f63c920f81a3bec8a50c68.jpg"},{"name":"White Feather","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/869840/9131d9843bf92d7879c5f623a923796fb457e220.jpg"},{"name":"New item for illumination","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/869840/dca263f385f8ba39e6f433f76b287b7cf4184dde.jpg"},{"name":"Cry","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/869840/9d81bf08662ac3c3c2ee10e7e1e320898c4eab10.jpg"},{"name":"Mistrust","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/869840/15c3ae4f3d78e65ddb2703484762aec232845758.jpg"},{"name":"BUG?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/869840/012d31bd5cd5ac74860ff6f63bea36c05e29e5b5.jpg"},{"name":"Candle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/869840/f12aae46f007f5b0515efc5741965e7e9eb14309.jpg"},{"name":"Curiosity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/869840/755dfe01709071b3a43bd91b38f265086b01f58a.jpg"},{"name":"Prophet","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/869840/ec53f956ff166d9e00148fb588c5b9597630966e.jpg"},{"name":"Wrong place to hide","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/869840/e6a231b7d6ad057ccf2740f2529ec492dce00c6d.jpg"}],"total":19},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728371084","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/page.bg.jpg?t=1728371084","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728371084","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728371084","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>Game Information</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Feather Of Praying&quot; is a horror puzzle RPG released in 2016, which has received numerous positive reviews since its launch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game was officially launched on Steam in 2018 and underwent a major update in 2024,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">adding new endings while also bringing new puzzle content and performance experiences.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u9898\u56fe\u6392\u7248-\u7fbd\u7ffc.png?t=1728371084\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201cI'll tell you another story.\u201d</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201cThis is a story about a girl and a wish.\u201d</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u201cA warm and romantic fairy tale\u2026\u201d</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u6807\u98981.png?t=1728371084\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a story about &quot;wishes&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interwoven with feelings of sadness and healing, where terrifying scenes blend with dreams.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u201cLet me fulfill your wish for you, but the corresponding price is\u2026\u201d</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, players will take on the role of a girl named Qiu Xiaoqi, waking up in a strange room. She will explore the mysterious room filled with puzzles alongside a mysterious young man with white hair, unraveling layers of mechanisms and uncovering the truth behind her loss of consciousness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u63d2\u56fe2.png?t=1728371084\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this journey full of choices and unknowns,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">players will face various challenges as they explore in a terrifying environment,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">experiencing the profound emotional journeys of the characters through memories and dreams, exploring the wishes hidden deep within their hearts.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Will this wish be fulfilled? How will this story unfold? Everything is for you to write\u2026</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u6807\u98982.png?t=1728371084\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u63d2\u56fe1.png?t=1728371084\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Immersive horror atmosphere</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every unknown fear draws you deeply into it.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Intricate puzzle design</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Creative mechanisms provide a unique exploration experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Heart-pounding storyline</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The profound emotional journeys of the characters present a moving tale.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rich sound performance</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Beautiful music and intense sound effects perfectly blend into the game atmosphere.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u6807\u98983.png?t=1728371084\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game Type:</strong> Horror Puzzle<br><strong>Number of Endings:</strong> 7 (*updated in 2024)<br><strong>Estimated Playtime: 2</strong>-4 hours</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Basic Controls:</strong><br>Movement: Arrow keys<br>Investigate/Confirm: Z/Space/Enter<br>Menu/Cancel: X/ESC<br>Save Management: F5<br>Resolution Adjustment: F6<br>Run: Shift</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u6807\u98984.png?t=1728371084\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game Author: \u79cb\u4e4b\u5fe7\u90c1</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game Artist: \u96e8\u516e</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game Publisher: Eternal Dream Studio</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For more staff, please see the in-game credits.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/extras/\u6807\u98985.png?t=1728371084\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is the first horror puzzle game I developed in 2016.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It was my first time making a horror puzzle game, so I hope everyone understands if there are any shortcomings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game does not contain any jump-scare CG flashes, so there\u2019s no need to worry about being startled by CG suddenly~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game has undergone multiple tests, but if there are any remaining bugs, please report them immediately.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feedback channel: <a href=\"mailto:413228337@qq.com\">413228337@qq.com</a></p>","developers":["\u79cb\u4e4b\u5fe7\u90c1"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/869840/header.jpg?t=1728371084","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"\u4e00\u3001\u6e38\u620f\u4e2d\u6240\u6709\u7acb\u7ed8\u3001CG\u7d20\u6750\u5747\u4e3a\u539f\u521b\uff0c\u672a\u7ecf\u5141\u8bb8\u7981\u6b62\u632a\u7528\u3002<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u4e8c\u3001\u7981\u6b62\u5bf9\u6e38\u620f\u8fdb\u884c\u89e3\u5305\uff0c\u4ee5\u53ca\u7531\u6b64\u884d\u751f\u7684\uff0c\u5305\u542b\u4e14\u4e0d\u9650\u4e8e\uff1a\u64c5\u81ea\u63d0\u53d6\u5e76\u632a\u7528\u3001\u53d1\u5e03\u6e38\u620f\u7684\u7d20\u6750\u8d44\u6e90\u7b49\u884c\u4e3a\u3002<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u4e09\u3001\u6e38\u620f\u4e2d\u5f15\u7528\u7684\u97f3\u4e50\u7d20\u6750\u8457\u4f5c\u6743\u5f52\u539f\u4f5c\u8005\u6240\u6709\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u9700\u8981\u4f7f\u7528\uff0c\u8bf7\u5230\u539f\u7ad9\u70b9\u81ea\u884c\u4e0b\u8f7d\u5e76\u6309\u7167\u4f7f\u7528\u89c4\u7ea6\u4f7f\u7528\u3002<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u56db\u3001\u7981\u6b62\u4efb\u4f55\u56e2\u4f53\u6216\u8005\u4e2a\u4eba\u5bf9\u6e38\u620f\u8fdb\u884c\u4e8c\u6b21\u53d1\u5e03\u3002<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u4e94\u3001\u8fdd\u53cd\u4e0a\u8ff0\u5